query:
UPDATE questions q
JOIN modules m ON q.moduleId = m.id
JOIN subjects s ON m.subjectId = s.id
SET q.subject = s.name,
    q.topic = m.name
WHERE q.subject IS NULL OR q.topic IS NULL
command:
